          <title>
            <string language="en">-le and -el Words</string>
            <string language="es">Palabras terminadas en –Ie y -eI</string>
            <string language="ga">Focail –le agus –el</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">- Le und - EL Wörter</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">- le et - mots de EL</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">- le e - palavras do EL</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">- le e - parole di EL</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">- LE και - λέξεις EL</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">Children identify the correct and incorrect spelling of -el and -le words, and then go on to use them to complete sentences.</string>
            <string language="es">Los niños han de identificar cuando se deletrean  correctamente las palabras terminadas en -eI e –Ie, y luego usarlas para completar frases.</string>
            <string language="ga">Sainaithníonn leanaí an litriú ceart ar fhocail ina bhfuil -el agus -le, agus ansin úsáideann siad iad chun abairtí a chríochnú.</string>
          </description>
          <language>en</language>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">English</string>
            <string language="es">Inglés. Hoja de trabajo</string>
            <string language="ga">Béarla</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Worksheet</string>
            <string language="ga">Bileog Oibre</string>
          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Kinder kennzeichnen die korrekte und falsche 
Rechtschreibung von - EL und - le words und fahren dann fort, sie zu 
benutzen, um Programmsätze durchzuführen.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les enfants identifient l'épellation correcte et 
incorrecte - EL et - de le words, et puis continuent pour les employer
pour terminer des phrases.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">As crianças identificam a soletração correta e 
incorreta - EL e - de le palavra, e vão então sobre usá-los 
terminar sentenças.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">I bambini identificano l'ortografia corretta ed 
errata - EL e - di le words ed allora continuano ad usarli per 
completare le frasi.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Τα παιδιά προσδιορίζουν τη σωστή και ανακριβή 
ορθογραφία - EL και - LE ωορδς, και πηγαίνουν έπειτα για να 
τους χρησιμοποιήσουν στις πλήρεις προτάσεις.</string>
          </description>
